{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-04-15-how-to-add-border-to-text-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends 👋, Welcome To aHoisting! To add border to text in react js, you can use inline css  and using css class  in . It will add border to text in react js…","html":"<p>Hi Friends 👋,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add border to text in react js, you can use inline css <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ border: '1px solid black'}}</code> and using css class <code class=\"language-text\">border: 1px solid black;</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">borderedText</code>. It will add border to text in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add border to text in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let’s start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import react component.</h3>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> </code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Create a Component.</h3>\n<p>you can use <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ border: '1px solid black'}}</code> and add border to text in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Using inline styles */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">border</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1px solid black'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">padding</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'5px'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Welcome To aHoisting<span class=\"token operator\">!</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Inline Style<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      \n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Using CSS class */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"borderedText\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Welcome To aHoisting<span class=\"token operator\">!</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span> Class<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Define the add border to text example.</h3>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">React</code> and use <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ border: '1px solid black'}}</code> to add border to text in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">TextWithBorder</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Using inline styles */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">border</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1px solid black'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">padding</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'5px'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Welcome To aHoisting<span class=\"token operator\">!</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Inline Style<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      \n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Using CSS class */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"borderedText\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Welcome To aHoisting<span class=\"token operator\">!</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span> Class<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> TextWithBorder<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.css</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.borderedText</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ border: '1px solid black'}}</code> css and add border to text in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e60209553c1a6f26/ec897/border-to-text.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.822784810126581%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRj4AAABXRUJQVlA4IDIAAACwAQCdASoUAAMAAsBMJZwAAudZt67gAP7zr/t+He5t0os1dfyfQWlKYWAO/JGC0cAAAA=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, border to text\"\n        title=\"React, add, border to text\"\n        src=\"/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e60209553c1a6f26/8aab1/border-to-text.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e60209553c1a6f26/81b7c/border-to-text.webp 158w,\n/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e60209553c1a6f26/6ea66/border-to-text.webp 315w,\n/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e60209553c1a6f26/8aab1/border-to-text.webp 630w,\n/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e60209553c1a6f26/a70f5/border-to-text.webp 945w,\n/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e60209553c1a6f26/4ef06/border-to-text.webp 1260w,\n/static/c712f2ff12a141d9e6020